1
00:00:30,950 --> 00:00:35,940
♪Your secret, dangerous flaws♪

2
00:00:36,250 --> 00:00:41,620
♪I can stay close
without seeing through♪

3
00:00:41,890 --> 00:00:45,610
♪As long as it's about love♪

4
00:00:45,710 --> 00:00:46,870
♪No matter how absurd♪

5
00:00:47,260 --> 00:00:51,450
♪I choose to get used to it♪

6
00:00:52,810 --> 00:00:56,900
♪Truth or lies, you decide what's true♪

7
00:00:56,970 --> 00:01:00,800
♪I won't overturn it anymore♪

8
00:01:01,040 --> 00:01:03,690
♪I cover my eyes and look♪

9
00:01:03,820 --> 00:01:07,860
♪Is love an abyss or a trap♪

10
00:01:07,960 --> 00:01:14,710
♪I only see the sparkle♪

11
00:01:33,220 --> 00:01:37,980
=Turbulent Love=

12
00:01:38,710 --> 00:01:39,980
How did they kidnap you?

13
00:01:39,980 --> 00:01:41,780
=Episode 14=
=The Truth Is Fake=

14
00:01:47,560 --> 00:01:48,400
I...

15
00:01:48,560 --> 00:01:50,280
I was just

16
00:01:51,920 --> 00:01:53,790
going to buy something,

17
00:01:55,350 --> 00:01:57,790
and then I took a shortcut.

18
00:02:02,480 --> 00:02:03,320
I'm sorry.

19
00:02:03,760 --> 00:02:04,600
It's okay.

20
00:02:05,680 --> 00:02:06,520
It's fine.

21
00:02:15,680 --> 00:02:17,590
Zhou Ziheng is
watching us closely lately.

22
00:02:18,080 --> 00:02:19,870
But the goods are moved to a safe place.

23
00:02:20,360 --> 00:02:22,190
Just set a time to deal with Mr. Suphan.

24
00:02:23,360 --> 00:02:24,240
But we need to hurry.

25
00:02:24,480 --> 00:02:25,470
The election is approaching.

26
00:02:25,930 --> 00:02:26,920
Uncle Kun is rushing too.

27
00:02:27,470 --> 00:02:29,030
Make it quick to avoid extra trouble.

28
00:02:30,280 --> 00:02:31,910
The trip to the UK
keeps getting delayed.

29
00:02:32,160 --> 00:02:33,150
I still want to take Hao Yu

30
00:02:33,150 --> 00:02:34,240
to see the snow for Christmas.

31
00:02:37,530 --> 00:02:38,840
Find out who was after the goods?

32
00:02:40,330 --> 00:02:41,360
It wasn't Yingquan's men.

33
00:02:41,750 --> 00:02:43,310
Suphan detained all of Yingquan's men.

34
00:02:44,190 --> 00:02:45,240
Counted all the casualties.

35
00:02:45,560 --> 00:02:46,520
And no one escaped.

36
00:02:50,470 --> 00:02:52,030
Yingquan isn't from Seronport.

37
00:02:52,520 --> 00:02:54,360
That's why he dares to make trouble.

38
00:02:56,080 --> 00:02:58,190
Who else but Yingquan dares to do this?

39
00:02:59,710 --> 00:03:00,680
Could it be Uncle Kun?

40
00:03:06,430 --> 00:03:08,150
Suphan offers the best price.

41
00:03:09,240 --> 00:03:10,520
He's running for councilor now.

42
00:03:10,800 --> 00:03:11,640
He wouldn't do that.

43
00:03:14,870 --> 00:03:15,870
You just said

44
00:03:15,870 --> 00:03:18,630
Suphan caught Yingquan's men.

45
00:03:20,190 --> 00:03:21,030
Then go ask

46
00:03:21,800 --> 00:03:23,190
who kidnapped Hao Yu that day

47
00:03:23,280 --> 00:03:24,120
and where.

48
00:03:25,360 --> 00:03:26,590
I already had Suphan ask them.

49
00:03:27,750 --> 00:03:28,590
No one confessed.

50
00:03:29,080 --> 00:03:30,240
Even torture didn't work.

51
00:03:31,560 --> 00:03:32,520
His trusted aide said

52
00:03:32,680 --> 00:03:33,750
someone dropped her off.

53
00:03:34,190 --> 00:03:35,080
The person was masked.

54
00:03:35,280 --> 00:03:36,120
They had no idea.

55
00:03:47,080 --> 00:03:48,630
Did you check all the surveillance

56
00:03:49,080 --> 00:03:50,360
near where Hao Yu was kidnapped?

57
00:03:50,800 --> 00:03:51,640
We did.

58
00:03:51,910 --> 00:03:53,080
But that area is a blind spot.

59
00:03:56,470 --> 00:03:58,080
Then go door to door.

60
00:03:59,150 --> 00:04:01,870
Check every shop thoroughly.

61
00:04:02,590 --> 00:04:03,960
Piece together the clues for me.

62
00:04:05,960 --> 00:04:06,800
By the way,

63
00:04:07,080 --> 00:04:07,920
where is Hao Yu?

64
00:04:08,430 --> 00:04:09,270
Why don't I see her?

65
00:04:09,710 --> 00:04:10,550
Feihu said

66
00:04:10,900 --> 00:04:12,560
Yu just had him take her
to a fortune teller.

67
00:04:12,760 --> 00:04:14,280
Said she hasn't been there
in a long time.

68
00:04:28,720 --> 00:04:30,360
Yu, are you sure you want to go?

69
00:04:30,870 --> 00:04:32,800
It's eerie and quite unlucky here.

70
00:04:33,160 --> 00:04:34,070
Besides, Guan...

71
00:04:35,950 --> 00:04:37,560
This... this is
where he had his accident.

72
00:04:39,480 --> 00:04:40,720
It's been so long.

73
00:04:41,560 --> 00:04:43,190
Besides, I'm here for a reason today.

74
00:04:44,680 --> 00:04:45,520
By the way,

75
00:04:46,560 --> 00:04:47,720
how did Uncle Kun

76
00:04:47,950 --> 00:04:49,270
catch him here before?

77
00:04:50,160 --> 00:04:51,000
You don't know?

78
00:04:51,210 --> 00:04:52,190
Zhijie didn't tell you?

79
00:04:54,040 --> 00:04:55,800
It's not my place to ask.

80
00:04:59,310 --> 00:05:00,560
But you asked the right person.

81
00:05:01,160 --> 00:05:03,040
Zhijie might not know as much as I do.

82
00:05:03,830 --> 00:05:04,690
Well, I...

83
00:05:04,720 --> 00:05:06,600
I heard it from Weihao
when he was drunk.

84
00:05:07,430 --> 00:05:10,750
He said Guan and Feishu
were meeting here,

85
00:05:11,040 --> 00:05:12,800
followed by the dirty cop
Uncle Kun set up.

86
00:05:13,090 --> 00:05:14,600
Then the cop called and told Uncle Kun.

87
00:05:16,480 --> 00:05:17,320
Followed?

88
00:05:30,340 --> 00:05:32,460
(Career: Worst luck,
Children: Medium luck)

89
00:05:32,480 --> 00:05:36,160
In mist-veiled towers,
demons are spying.

90
00:05:38,160 --> 00:05:41,950
A beauty bound by gilded chains.

91
00:05:44,000 --> 00:05:47,070
A ray of light breaks chaos.

92
00:05:48,390 --> 00:05:50,120
Rebirth from ruin

93
00:05:51,600 --> 00:05:53,190
brings good omens.

94
00:05:56,040 --> 00:05:59,390
Are you praying for a child again, Miss?

95
00:06:02,360 --> 00:06:03,200
No.

96
00:06:03,750 --> 00:06:04,590
For my career.

97
00:06:07,310 --> 00:06:08,870
Praying for a child has decent luck.

98
00:06:09,800 --> 00:06:10,800
But for your career,

99
00:06:11,750 --> 00:06:13,560
it's another worst-luck slip.

100
00:06:16,040 --> 00:06:17,800
The first two lines of this fortune slip

101
00:06:18,160 --> 00:06:21,390
mean you're trapped by false affection.

102
00:06:22,800 --> 00:06:25,190
Miss, have you recently felt like

103
00:06:25,270 --> 00:06:26,630
you're in a fog?

104
00:06:27,000 --> 00:06:28,720
Like you can't hold onto anything?

105
00:06:40,120 --> 00:06:42,310
Ziheng got transferred back.

106
00:06:43,480 --> 00:06:44,320
Is he...

107
00:06:46,430 --> 00:06:47,270
doing okay?

108
00:06:48,720 --> 00:06:49,560
Hard to say.

109
00:06:50,270 --> 00:06:51,110
Same, I guess.

110
00:06:51,720 --> 00:06:52,560
But not really.

111
00:06:53,270 --> 00:06:54,270
Maybe the promotion

112
00:06:54,720 --> 00:06:55,560
made him more steady.

113
00:06:56,800 --> 00:06:57,640
You guys...

114
00:07:02,040 --> 00:07:03,000
Police colleagues said

115
00:07:03,720 --> 00:07:06,120
Liang Zhaokun had his men
follow me here.

116
00:07:07,040 --> 00:07:08,120
When I got the call that day,

117
00:07:09,530 --> 00:07:10,380
I was first

118
00:07:10,390 --> 00:07:11,800
on the scene.

119
00:07:13,360 --> 00:07:15,240
I saw Ji Zhijie rushing you away.

120
00:07:21,750 --> 00:07:23,000
This "first"...

121
00:07:23,510 --> 00:07:24,950
was almost the exact same time.

122
00:07:26,160 --> 00:07:28,040
Who's the dirty cop
working with Liang Zhaokun?

123
00:07:34,070 --> 00:07:34,910
I'm sorry.

124
00:07:36,480 --> 00:07:37,510
We're still investigating.

125
00:07:38,530 --> 00:07:40,190
I asked the master here
to pass a message.

126
00:07:40,190 --> 00:07:41,310
Didn't you get it?

127
00:07:43,920 --> 00:07:44,760
No.

128
00:07:46,430 --> 00:07:48,160
You want to
get away from Ji Zhijie soon.

129
00:07:48,500 --> 00:07:49,600
And get your freedom back, right?

130
00:07:51,630 --> 00:07:52,920
Where are the goods?

131
00:07:54,560 --> 00:07:55,630
How did you find me?

132
00:07:59,160 --> 00:08:00,000
I told you

133
00:08:01,190 --> 00:08:03,070
we have more than one
mole and informant.

134
00:08:12,000 --> 00:08:12,870
If anything happens,

135
00:08:12,870 --> 00:08:14,000
I'll find a way to contact you.

136
00:08:14,390 --> 00:08:15,230
Hao Yu.

137
00:08:34,320 --> 00:08:35,160
Godfather.

138
00:08:39,480 --> 00:08:40,320
I'm sorry.

139
00:08:44,360 --> 00:08:46,200
I was too careless.

140
00:08:48,440 --> 00:08:49,870
I was completely blind.

141
00:08:52,190 --> 00:08:53,030
I always thought

142
00:08:53,030 --> 00:08:54,840
he was different now.

143
00:08:58,000 --> 00:08:59,200
But I didn't expect

144
00:08:59,200 --> 00:09:00,720
to trust the wrong person.

145
00:09:02,480 --> 00:09:03,750
In this world,

146
00:09:06,910 --> 00:09:08,910
black might not turn white.

147
00:09:11,750 --> 00:09:12,840
But I forgot

148
00:09:12,840 --> 00:09:14,550
that white can turn black.

149
00:09:18,200 --> 00:09:19,670
I never figured out

150
00:09:19,670 --> 00:09:21,080
what he was really up to.

151
00:09:23,750 --> 00:09:25,320
But now I know.

152
00:09:28,120 --> 00:09:30,150
If he's really

153
00:09:31,120 --> 00:09:32,390
the dirty cop Liang Zhaokun planted

154
00:09:34,150 --> 00:09:35,630
and the accomplice who hurt you,

155
00:09:37,510 --> 00:09:38,870
no matter what it takes,

156
00:09:38,910 --> 00:09:40,360
I will avenge you.

157
00:09:41,870 --> 00:09:43,840
I won't let any of them get away.

158
00:09:54,870 --> 00:09:57,120
Although this is a worst-luck slip,

159
00:09:57,120 --> 00:09:58,510
(Worst-luck)

160
00:09:58,510 --> 00:10:00,910
read the last two lines.

161
00:10:00,910 --> 00:10:02,080
(A ray of light breaks chaos.
Rebirth from ruin brings good omens.)

162
00:10:02,080 --> 00:10:03,630
That is the key
to breaking the deadlock.

163
00:10:04,720 --> 00:10:07,360
Miss, you know of
nirvana and rebirth, right?

164
00:10:09,120 --> 00:10:10,790
As long as you realize it in time,

165
00:10:11,440 --> 00:10:13,120
there's still room
to turn things around.

166
00:10:15,000 --> 00:10:16,390
When you hit rock bottom,

167
00:10:17,360 --> 00:10:18,720
new life will emerge.

168
00:10:20,910 --> 00:10:24,080
That ray of light in a seeming dead end

169
00:10:25,510 --> 00:10:28,790
is the turning point to clear the fog.

170
00:10:45,320 --> 00:10:46,160
Hao Yu.

171
00:10:47,870 --> 00:10:50,360
I have some things to wrap up lately.

172
00:10:51,200 --> 00:10:52,120
Once they're handled,

173
00:10:53,720 --> 00:10:54,600
I'll do the handover.

174
00:10:56,960 --> 00:10:57,800
I originally planned

175
00:10:57,810 --> 00:11:00,200
to finish
before Uncle Kun's 60th birthday.

176
00:11:00,910 --> 00:11:02,120
As a big gift for him.

177
00:11:02,960 --> 00:11:04,320
But the closer it gets,

178
00:11:04,340 --> 00:11:05,440
the more attention it draws.

179
00:11:08,550 --> 00:11:09,480
But I promise you,

180
00:11:10,120 --> 00:11:10,960
in a few more days,

181
00:11:12,510 --> 00:11:14,790
I'll take you to the UK
for Christmas and snow.

182
00:11:15,120 --> 00:11:15,960
Okay?

183
00:11:19,120 --> 00:11:19,960
Okay.

184
00:11:20,480 --> 00:11:21,630
Then I'll handle

185
00:11:21,750 --> 00:11:23,240
some things of my own these two days.

186
00:11:26,510 --> 00:11:27,350
The Lounge?

187
00:11:33,080 --> 00:11:34,440
You just mentioned

188
00:11:35,270 --> 00:11:37,000
Uncle Kun's 60th birthday.

189
00:11:38,080 --> 00:11:39,440
Such an important day.

190
00:11:40,200 --> 00:11:42,120
Will all his adopted kids be there?

191
00:11:44,300 --> 00:11:46,080
Actually, he doesn't plan to
make a big fuss.

192
00:11:46,670 --> 00:11:48,790
Since he's running for
councilor recently,

193
00:11:48,850 --> 00:11:49,960
he wants to keep a low profile.

194
00:11:51,270 --> 00:11:52,200
But

195
00:11:52,500 --> 00:11:54,200
almost everyone from Cangfeng
will be there.

196
00:11:55,600 --> 00:11:57,320
We'll just give a gift and have a meal.

197
00:11:59,480 --> 00:12:00,750
Then let me prepare

198
00:12:00,750 --> 00:12:01,910
the birthday gift for you.

199
00:12:06,480 --> 00:12:08,260
Why are you being so nice to me
all of a sudden?

200
00:12:15,550 --> 00:12:17,480
You never used to

201
00:12:17,720 --> 00:12:19,080
care about these things.

202
00:12:23,080 --> 00:12:25,510
I just think since we're leaving soon,

203
00:12:27,720 --> 00:12:29,630
it's better to make peace than enemies.

204
00:12:31,630 --> 00:12:33,960
I can play the good Yu one last time.

205
00:12:34,240 --> 00:12:35,200
And do your filial part.

206
00:12:39,270 --> 00:12:40,360
What do you plan to give?

207
00:12:44,440 --> 00:12:46,360
The councilor position he wants most.

208
00:12:46,360 --> 00:12:48,030
You'll give him that soon enough.

209
00:12:49,000 --> 00:12:50,440
As for

210
00:12:50,550 --> 00:12:52,200
rare delicacies,

211
00:12:53,000 --> 00:12:54,550
sports cars and beautiful women,

212
00:12:55,000 --> 00:12:55,960
he doesn't lack any of them.

213
00:12:56,510 --> 00:12:57,790
And so many people give him those.

214
00:12:58,080 --> 00:12:59,150
It'll be tacky.

215
00:13:00,870 --> 00:13:02,200
Didn't you always say

216
00:13:02,720 --> 00:13:04,390
that the fragrance in my room

217
00:13:04,790 --> 00:13:05,790
is your favorite?

218
00:13:06,030 --> 00:13:06,870
It helps you sleep.

219
00:13:08,870 --> 00:13:09,840
Then I'll give him that.

220
00:13:09,910 --> 00:13:11,440
Plus whatever you want to give him.

221
00:13:11,840 --> 00:13:13,870
It's both thoughtful and grand.

222
00:13:14,440 --> 00:13:15,280
What do you think?

223
00:13:20,480 --> 00:13:21,360
What?

224
00:13:22,550 --> 00:13:23,790
Are you afraid I'll poison it?

225
00:13:29,720 --> 00:13:30,720
I just feel like

226
00:13:33,810 --> 00:13:35,030
you're being nicer and nicer to me.

227
00:15:22,960 --> 00:15:23,800
Uncle Kun.

228
00:15:24,120 --> 00:15:25,270
Years ago you told me

229
00:15:25,600 --> 00:15:27,510
that in the underworld,
it's about deals, not lives.

230
00:15:28,670 --> 00:15:29,630
Today is your birthday.

231
00:15:31,270 --> 00:15:32,110
This toast

232
00:15:33,390 --> 00:15:34,790
is to you leading Cangfeng

233
00:15:35,240 --> 00:15:37,440
from the streets to the halls of power.

234
00:15:38,200 --> 00:15:39,550
May you get what you wish for

235
00:15:40,870 --> 00:15:42,630
and win the councilor position.

236
00:15:49,960 --> 00:15:51,370
Cangfeng shall never fall!

237
00:15:52,480 --> 00:15:54,000
Cangfeng shall never fall!

238
00:15:54,720 --> 00:15:56,200
Cangfeng shall never fall!

239
00:16:15,740 --> 00:16:18,300
(Wish you lifelong health and radiant days.
Sincerely, Ji Zhijie.)

240
00:16:23,180 --> 00:16:24,900
(Birthday gift for Mr. Liang Zhaokun)

241
00:16:36,750 --> 00:16:37,600
You drank so much.

242
00:16:38,360 --> 00:16:39,320
Alright, alright, alright.

243
00:16:39,550 --> 00:16:40,390
Let's go home.

244
00:16:41,600 --> 00:16:42,440
I'm not drunk.

245
00:16:44,670 --> 00:16:45,510
Come on.

246
00:16:45,720 --> 00:16:46,630
Let's go home.

247
00:16:49,750 --> 00:16:51,230
Okay, careful.

248
00:16:55,670 --> 00:16:56,510
Feihu.

249
00:16:56,910 --> 00:16:57,910
You take him back first.

250
00:16:58,080 --> 00:16:58,920
He's so drunk.

251
00:16:59,720 --> 00:17:01,120
Tell Chen and the others

252
00:17:01,150 --> 00:17:02,200
to make him sobering soup.

253
00:17:02,960 --> 00:17:04,200
I have an event at the orphanage.

254
00:17:04,350 --> 00:17:05,200
I need to head over.

255
00:17:05,820 --> 00:17:06,880
Let me drop you off first.

256
00:17:07,050 --> 00:17:08,040
Then I'll take Zhijie home.

257
00:17:08,570 --> 00:17:09,680
- I'm worried...
- No need.

258
00:17:10,400 --> 00:17:12,310
I'll just grab a cab there myself.

259
00:17:13,110 --> 00:17:14,590
With so many people outside Cangfeng,

260
00:17:14,600 --> 00:17:15,720
no one would dare cause trouble.

261
00:17:16,720 --> 00:17:17,920
Alright, you should go now.

262
00:17:18,030 --> 00:17:18,870
He's drunk.

263
00:17:18,960 --> 00:17:19,800
Okay.

264
00:17:20,750 --> 00:17:21,590
Let's go.

265
00:17:36,700 --> 00:17:39,300
(Wish you lifelong health and radiant days.
Sincerely, Ji Zhijie.)

266
00:17:45,640 --> 00:17:46,480
Let me do it.

267
00:17:52,070 --> 00:17:52,910
Uncle Kun.

268
00:17:54,550 --> 00:17:56,240
I swapped shifts just to come here.

269
00:17:56,720 --> 00:17:58,750
But I'm sorry I can't

270
00:17:59,620 --> 00:18:00,640
congratulate you in person.

271
00:18:07,440 --> 00:18:08,280
However,

272
00:18:08,920 --> 00:18:10,880
I still wish you a successful election.

273
00:18:11,750 --> 00:18:13,200
I hope to serve you in the future

274
00:18:13,400 --> 00:18:14,240
under your protection.

275
00:18:18,200 --> 00:18:19,480
You really put thought into this.

276
00:18:20,070 --> 00:18:20,920
I heard

277
00:18:21,510 --> 00:18:23,720
you raided
Yingquan's territory last time

278
00:18:24,960 --> 00:18:26,480
and even arrested Zhijie.

279
00:18:27,750 --> 00:18:29,070
Lucky the goods are safe.

280
00:18:33,590 --> 00:18:36,030
I... I was on duty when I got the call.

281
00:18:36,400 --> 00:18:37,240
I had to go.

282
00:18:40,350 --> 00:18:42,440
I barely let them take the goods.

283
00:18:42,800 --> 00:18:44,110
Bringing them back for questioning

284
00:18:44,210 --> 00:18:45,150
was just a routine check.

285
00:18:45,770 --> 00:18:47,070
That way, no one gets suspicious.

286
00:18:49,070 --> 00:18:49,910
But...

287
00:18:50,440 --> 00:18:51,640
I was just following protocol.

288
00:18:52,160 --> 00:18:53,440
I released them soon after.

289
00:18:54,070 --> 00:18:55,160
- Really?
- Yes.

290
00:19:07,640 --> 00:19:08,480
Uncle Kun.

291
00:19:08,830 --> 00:19:10,830
I really had no choice last time.

292
00:19:13,240 --> 00:19:15,110
I won't make the same mistake again.

293
00:19:18,160 --> 00:19:19,830
You've earned some credit this time.

294
00:19:20,960 --> 00:19:22,240
You did very well.

295
00:19:22,640 --> 00:19:23,750
When the time is right,

296
00:19:24,880 --> 00:19:26,590
I'll definitely reinstate you.

297
00:19:32,550 --> 00:19:33,390
Well,

298
00:19:34,000 --> 00:19:34,990
if there's nothing else,

299
00:19:35,000 --> 00:19:36,030
off to the police station.

300
00:19:50,960 --> 00:19:52,480
Hello? Where are you?

301
00:19:54,200 --> 00:19:55,190
I'm at the police station

302
00:20:01,720 --> 00:20:03,070
I know where the goods are.

303
00:20:05,000 --> 00:20:06,240
Where is it? Tell me now.

304
00:20:07,350 --> 00:20:08,440
Let's talk in person.

305
00:20:11,960 --> 00:20:12,800
Okay.

306
00:20:27,240 --> 00:20:28,510
Why are we meeting here?

307
00:20:31,000 --> 00:20:32,000
With our identities now,

308
00:20:32,000 --> 00:20:33,070
meeting here is very sensitive.

309
00:20:33,330 --> 00:20:34,320
We could easily be exposed.

310
00:20:38,400 --> 00:20:39,590
If someone sees us...

311
00:20:43,110 --> 00:20:44,350
Besides us,

312
00:20:44,920 --> 00:20:46,110
everyone else here is dead.

313
00:20:48,000 --> 00:20:48,950
The only ones who are afraid

314
00:20:49,920 --> 00:20:51,350
are those with a guilty conscience.

315
00:21:09,160 --> 00:21:11,110
Today is godfather's birthday.

316
00:21:14,200 --> 00:21:15,720
It's also Liang Zhaokun's birthday.

317
00:21:21,240 --> 00:21:22,080
What a coincidence.

318
00:21:24,880 --> 00:21:26,640
A demon and an angel

319
00:21:26,640 --> 00:21:27,960
born on the exact same day.

320
00:21:30,400 --> 00:21:31,240
Right?

321
00:21:33,510 --> 00:21:34,750
Hell is empty

322
00:21:35,750 --> 00:21:37,000
and all the devils are here.

323
00:21:39,030 --> 00:21:40,350
Well, if they were

324
00:21:40,790 --> 00:21:42,270
both in the crowd,

325
00:21:43,240 --> 00:21:44,200
how could you tell

326
00:21:44,200 --> 00:21:45,960
who's real and who's a ghost?

327
00:21:47,590 --> 00:21:48,430
I'm sorry.

328
00:21:49,160 --> 00:21:50,000
I've been so busy.

329
00:21:51,530 --> 00:21:53,200
I just had a meeting
at the police station.

330
00:21:54,000 --> 00:21:55,030
So I didn't bring anything.

331
00:22:29,350 --> 00:22:30,190
It's fine.

332
00:22:31,920 --> 00:22:33,270
Godfather's spirit in heaven

333
00:22:34,880 --> 00:22:36,510
will always watch over you

334
00:22:38,110 --> 00:22:39,000
and protect you.

335
00:22:40,920 --> 00:22:42,640
He will surely understand you.

336
00:22:47,750 --> 00:22:48,720
Do you still remember

337
00:22:50,510 --> 00:22:52,160
how godfather died?

338
00:22:54,030 --> 00:22:54,870
Of course.

339
00:22:56,030 --> 00:22:57,160
I'll never forget.

340
00:22:58,360 --> 00:23:00,030
(Guan Renjie)
This is what the seniors taught us.

341
00:23:02,240 --> 00:23:03,240
Everything we do

342
00:23:04,640 --> 00:23:06,070
isn't it to uphold justice?

343
00:23:12,920 --> 00:23:13,760
By the way,

344
00:23:14,230 --> 00:23:15,110
you said on the phone

345
00:23:15,110 --> 00:23:16,240
you know where the goods are.

346
00:23:25,070 --> 00:23:27,240
Ji Zhijie's goods are
at Li Island's dock.

347
00:23:39,720 --> 00:23:40,560
Uncle Kun.

348
00:23:41,640 --> 00:23:42,480
Uncle Kun.

349
00:23:43,030 --> 00:23:43,870
Look at this.

350
00:23:49,070 --> 00:23:50,350
This seems to be...

351
00:23:54,880 --> 00:23:55,720
What about the time?

352
00:23:57,640 --> 00:23:59,550
I'm not sure about the time,

353
00:24:00,110 --> 00:24:01,480
but I'm certain of the location.

354
00:24:04,920 --> 00:24:06,480
Knowing the location is good enough.

355
00:24:06,880 --> 00:24:07,720
Good job.

356
00:24:08,960 --> 00:24:09,960
Let me know

357
00:24:10,440 --> 00:24:11,430
when you find out the time.

358
00:24:11,720 --> 00:24:12,750
I'll go set things up now.

359
00:24:13,240 --> 00:24:14,080
I'll leave first.

360
00:24:19,880 --> 00:24:21,310
Why is there no sound yet?

361
00:24:21,830 --> 00:24:22,670
Almost there.

362
00:24:30,270 --> 00:24:31,110
Zhou Ziheng.

363
00:24:35,920 --> 00:24:37,350
May our revenge succeed.

364
00:24:50,070 --> 00:24:51,440
To keep you from being exposed,

365
00:24:52,960 --> 00:24:54,030
I played along with you

366
00:24:54,590 --> 00:24:55,790
to frame Weihao.

367
00:24:56,680 --> 00:24:57,750
Then I destroyed the data

368
00:24:58,030 --> 00:24:59,000
and framed Zhong Jiali.

369
00:25:00,070 --> 00:25:02,920
I risked my life to apply for a
special mission from the police station

370
00:25:03,030 --> 00:25:03,870
to catch Ji Zhijie.

371
00:25:05,920 --> 00:25:07,680
All to take down Cangfeng.

372
00:25:08,750 --> 00:25:09,790
I even got injured

373
00:25:10,240 --> 00:25:11,080
and demoted.

374
00:25:13,400 --> 00:25:14,240
Everything I did

375
00:25:15,960 --> 00:25:17,640
was to hide your identity
as an informant.

376
00:25:18,110 --> 00:25:19,310
So Cangfeng wouldn't find out.

377
00:25:23,240 --> 00:25:25,160
This ungrateful dog!

378
00:25:29,440 --> 00:25:30,550
Even a dog I raise

379
00:25:31,440 --> 00:25:32,790
knows how to wag its tail.

380
00:25:36,240 --> 00:25:38,480
A dog wouldn't use the bone I gave it

381
00:25:39,640 --> 00:25:41,310
to stab me in the back!

382
00:25:44,480 --> 00:25:45,320
I...

383
00:25:46,110 --> 00:25:47,880
gave you everything,

384
00:25:52,510 --> 00:25:55,310
yet you stabbed me in the back

385
00:25:56,000 --> 00:25:57,240
with my own kindness!

386
00:26:04,000 --> 00:26:05,480
Incense... Incense...

387
00:26:05,720 --> 00:26:06,560
Incense.

388
00:26:22,440 --> 00:26:25,350
That ray of light in a seeming dead end

389
00:26:26,400 --> 00:26:29,550
is the turning point to clear the fog.

390
00:26:38,550 --> 00:26:41,400
If I want to sleep for a long time,

391
00:26:43,000 --> 00:26:45,550
which incense should I use?

392
00:26:48,440 --> 00:26:49,280
This is the one...

393
00:26:52,400 --> 00:26:54,110
the one Hao Yu gave!

394
00:26:55,720 --> 00:26:58,000
She and Zhou Ziheng,

395
00:26:59,680 --> 00:27:00,590
that wild dog...

396
00:27:01,480 --> 00:27:02,400
are also connected.

397
00:27:02,880 --> 00:27:04,030
They are connected!

398
00:27:09,510 --> 00:27:10,750
Uncle Kun. Uncle Kun!

399
00:27:11,550 --> 00:27:12,390
Somebody help!

400
00:27:12,400 --> 00:27:13,240
Feiyu!

401
00:27:13,440 --> 00:27:14,280
Somebody help!

402
00:27:23,480 --> 00:27:24,320
Godfather.

403
00:27:27,200 --> 00:27:28,040
Back then,

404
00:27:28,880 --> 00:27:30,880
I entered Cangfeng alone for revenge.

405
00:27:33,920 --> 00:27:35,640
You were the ones who told me

406
00:27:37,240 --> 00:27:38,830
you'd clear my parents' names

407
00:27:41,070 --> 00:27:42,880
and give me the justice I wanted.

408
00:27:45,550 --> 00:27:46,550
I listened to you.

409
00:27:50,880 --> 00:27:52,000
For all these years,

410
00:27:54,350 --> 00:27:56,920
I've actively cooperated with you

411
00:27:59,030 --> 00:28:00,110
to find evidence.

412
00:28:11,400 --> 00:28:12,270
You're gone.

413
00:28:15,880 --> 00:28:17,350
Though my abilities are limited,

414
00:28:21,070 --> 00:28:23,070
I've always tried so hard.

415
00:28:24,480 --> 00:28:25,320
So hard.

416
00:28:26,480 --> 00:28:28,590
Tried everything I could

417
00:28:28,640 --> 00:28:31,070
to bring them all to justice.

418
00:28:37,270 --> 00:28:39,750
I never expected to
wrongly trust Zhou Ziheng.

419
00:28:42,640 --> 00:28:44,270
Now I finally understand.

420
00:28:47,270 --> 00:28:48,110
Only under

421
00:28:50,160 --> 00:28:51,110
order

422
00:28:51,880 --> 00:28:53,720
can we talk about justice and law.

423
00:28:58,440 --> 00:28:59,510
But Seronport

424
00:29:00,550 --> 00:29:02,200
isn't that kind of place anymore.

425
00:29:06,440 --> 00:29:07,830
You have to forgive me.

426
00:29:13,590 --> 00:29:15,070
Please forgive me.

427
00:29:17,590 --> 00:29:18,430
This time,

428
00:29:20,400 --> 00:29:21,750
if I miss this chance,

429
00:29:23,510 --> 00:29:25,310
I might never get another one.

430
00:29:31,310 --> 00:29:32,720
Never again.

431
00:29:35,960 --> 00:29:37,310
I had no other choice.

432
00:30:04,070 --> 00:30:04,910
Let me do it.

433
00:30:18,880 --> 00:30:21,750
A demon and an angel
born on the exact same day.

434
00:30:22,550 --> 00:30:23,790
Hell is empty

435
00:30:24,720 --> 00:30:26,030
and all the devils are here.

436
00:30:26,680 --> 00:30:28,680
Well, if they were both in the crowd,

437
00:30:30,510 --> 00:30:31,480
how could you tell

438
00:30:31,590 --> 00:30:33,400
who's real and who's a ghost?

439
00:30:34,510 --> 00:30:35,590
Do you still remember

440
00:30:37,350 --> 00:30:39,000
how godfather died?

441
00:30:40,070 --> 00:30:41,440
May our revenge succeed.

442
00:30:57,100 --> 00:30:58,080
Search over here first.

443
00:31:10,150 --> 00:31:14,910
♪Don't take amber from my eyes♪

444
00:31:16,790 --> 00:31:20,910
♪I'm scared you'll be swallowed by dark♪

445
00:31:22,350 --> 00:31:24,670
♪Watching you get tied down♪

446
00:31:24,670 --> 00:31:26,790
♪Trapped in the corner♪

447
00:31:26,830 --> 00:31:29,310
♪My heart feels torn apart♪

448
00:31:29,590 --> 00:31:34,910
♪Even if it's an abyss, I'll fall♪

449
00:31:36,790 --> 00:31:40,190
♪Gray fireworks♪

450
00:31:40,430 --> 00:31:43,510
♪Pushing back the bright corners♪

451
00:31:43,910 --> 00:31:47,070
♪Waiting for you to wakeup♪

452
00:31:47,070 --> 00:31:50,790
♪Hurts me too much♪

453
00:31:50,990 --> 00:31:54,270
♪I'm not afraid of the pain♪

454
00:31:54,270 --> 00:31:58,030
♪Even if I turn to dust for you♪

455
00:31:58,470 --> 00:32:00,790
♪Let the neon lights shatter and fall♪

456
00:32:00,950 --> 00:32:05,230
♪Filling every desolate corner♪

457
00:32:05,430 --> 00:32:08,630
♪Don't leave me to survive alone♪

458
00:32:08,630 --> 00:32:12,510
♪Still scared, I erase my wrongs♪

459
00:32:12,990 --> 00:32:18,830
♪I pray and confess through pain♪

460
00:32:21,390 --> 00:32:24,310
♪I learned to let go of myself♪

461
00:32:25,070 --> 00:32:27,830
♪I burn away every bitter result♪

462
00:32:27,830 --> 00:32:29,430
♪Just to light♪

463
00:32:29,590 --> 00:32:33,590
♪Eternal fireworks for you♪

464
00:32:34,150 --> 00:32:37,270
♪I'm not afraid of the pain♪

465
00:32:37,270 --> 00:32:41,110
♪Even if I turn to dust for you♪

466
00:32:41,470 --> 00:32:43,790
♪Let the neon lights shatter and fall♪

467
00:32:43,950 --> 00:32:48,230
♪Filling every desolate corner♪

468
00:32:48,430 --> 00:32:51,590
♪Don't leave me to survive alone♪

469
00:32:51,590 --> 00:32:55,590
♪Still scared, I erase my wrongs♪

470
00:32:55,990 --> 00:33:01,710
♪I pray and confess through pain♪
